1433	// CommitTracker commits beads.jsonl if it has uncommitted changes. Acquires
1434	// withTrackerLock so concurrent callers serialize on the parent .git index.
1435	// Callers already holding the lock must use commitTrackerLocked instead —
1436	// the lock is not re-entrant.
